  <description>
    <p>
      SmartSynchronize is a multi-platform file and directory compare tool. It allows you to compare
      files or perform 3-way-merges, both with the ability to edit the file contents.
    </p>
    <p>
      SmartSynchronize is optimized for comparing directory structures (for example, of software
      projects), and can keep them synchronized.
    </p>
